      <description>When you choose a basement remodeling system there are several questions you should ask from your contractor. Here are some of them: How long will it take your basement remodeling completely finished? By the best remodeling systems ceiling, flooring and wall system are done , with all necessary electrical work within two weeks. This increases [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://basementdesignpro.com"&gt;Basement Design&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get basement remodeling tips, ideas and informations.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-remodeling/basement-remodeling-system/"&gt;Basement Remodeling System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/basement-design/Basement_Design-Basement_Remodeling_System.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>When you choose a <em><a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-design/basement-remodeling-software/" >basement remodeling</a> system</em> there are several questions you should ask from your contractor.</p>
<p>Here are some of them:</p>
<h3>How long will it take your basement remodeling completely finished?</h3>
<p>By the best remodeling systems ceiling, flooring and wall system are done , with all necessary  electrical work within two weeks. This increases if you plan a bathroom in the basement, because water system and other belongings need more work.</p>
<h3>Is the remodeling system only contains wall installation?</h3>
<p>There are <a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-design/basement-remodeling-software/" >basement remodeling</a> systems that only contains wall installation and you have to contract with other contractors for electrical, plumbing, flooring and other activities during <a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-design/basement-finishing-ideas/" >basement finishing</a>.</p>
<p>So be sure to choose a contractor that do a turn key project for you. If necessary the contractor makes underpinning contracts so you have not have to be deal with them.</p>
<h3>What are the possible ceiling choices?</h3>
<p>With the best basement remodeling systems there are choices. You can have custom solution including brass and chrome grids, wood ceilings and other possibilities.</p>
<h3>What flooring solutions are the most frequent?</h3>
<p>Carpet, ceramic and wood. Flooring takes approximately a day if the floor is properly prepared.</p>
<h3>What about labor and material warranties?</h3>
<p>Always ask for them. The best contractors carry 5-10 years material and labor warranties for their remodeling system.</p>
<p>Do not contract with anybody for shorter warranty period.</p>
<h3>What does a green basement mean?</h3>
<p>The so called green solutions contains recycled or eco-friendly materials. Ask for them before your project. Ask the contractor what kind of material do it use and check them in Google.</p>
<p>There are hundreds of other questions can be asked when a <strong>basement remodeling system</strong> is chosen so come back later to this blog and read about other important questions.</p>
<p><strong><em> </em></strong></p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://basementdesignpro.com">Basement Design</a> blog where you can get basement remodeling tips, ideas and informations.<br/><br/><a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-remodeling/basement-remodeling-system/">Basement Remodeling System</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
