      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://basementdesignpro.com/?p=458</guid>
      <description>I have just read a basement design related article in Courierpress, that Eugenia and Maricela have turned a room in their basement into a mexican style party central, a perfect place for the fiestas they love. They wanted a space with the energy, warmth and flavor of a Mexican cantina, and they wanted it to reflect their Mexican-Canadian heritage. They [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://basementdesignpro.com"&gt;Basement Design&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get basement remodeling tips, ideas and informations.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-design/party-central-basement/"&gt;Party central in the basement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/basement-design/Basement_Design-Party_central_in_the_basement.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I have just read <a href="http://www.courierpress.com/news/2010/apr/01/divine-design-boring-basement-convivial-cantina/">a basement design related article in Courierpress</a>, that Eugenia and Maricela have turned a room in their basement into a mexican style party central, a perfect place for the fiestas they love.</p>
<p>They wanted a space with the energy, warmth and flavor of a Mexican cantina, and they wanted it to reflect their Mexican-Canadian heritage.</p>
<p>They have created a satellite kitchen for serving the dancing guests.  Highlighting this kitchen area is a cool, transparent globe light fixture.</p>
<p>They have used incredible and vibrant colors of Mexican on textiles, tiles, paints, fabrics and furnitures.</p>
<p>Covering the small window behind the sofa with a full, wall-sized, translucent blind gives the impression that the window is much larger than it is.  What a fantastic idea!</p>
<p>Well, this basement room is a great example of creativity, energy, fun and warm feelings.</p>
<p>You can see <a href="http://www.courierpress.com/news/2010/apr/01/divine-design-boring-basement-convivial-cantina/">a picture of their lovely basement </a>here.</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://basementdesignpro.com">Basement Design</a> blog where you can get basement remodeling tips, ideas and informations.<br/><br/><a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-design/party-central-basement/">Party central in the basement</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
