      <description>In every basement remodeling project one of the main question is how to estimate basement remodeling costs. First, you can find calculators on the internet. Just type &amp;#8220;basement remodeling estimate calculator&amp;#8221; or a similar keyword phrase into Google and you can find some handy tool quickly. Another possibility is to get a basement design software that contains [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://basementdesignpro.com"&gt;Basement Design&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get basement remodeling tips, ideas and informations.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-remodeling/basement-remodeling-estimate/"&gt;How To Estimate Basement Remodeling?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;



Similar basement designing news:&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-remodeling/basement-remodeling-system/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Basement Remodeling System'&gt;Basement Remodeling System&lt;/a&gt; &lt;small&gt;When you choose a basement remodeling system there are several...&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/basement-design/Basement_Design-How_To_Estimate_Basement_Remodeling.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In every <a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-design/basement-remodeling-software/" >basement remodeling</a> project one of the main question is how to estimate <a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basement-design/basement-remodeling-software/" >basement remodeling</a> costs.</p>
<p>First, you can find calculators on the internet. Just type &#8220;basement remodeling estimate calculator&#8221; or a similar keyword phrase into Google and you can find some handy tool quickly.</p>
<p>Another possibility is to get a <a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/basementdesignguide/"  rel='nofollow' >basement design</a> <a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/designsoftware/"  rel='nofollow' >software</a> that contains a cost estimation module.  So when you try to decide which designer program should you choose, a very important factor can be if it is have a cost calculation module or not.</p>
<p>If you are not satisfied with the internet cost calculation tools or do not want to buy a basement designer <a href="http://basementdesignpro.com/designsoftware/"  rel='nofollow' >software</a> there are at least two other choice.</p>
<p>Ask proposals from 3-5 local basement remodeling contractors for your planned project and compare them. Drop out the most and less expensive ones and calculate a main value from the remaining cost proposals.</p>
<p>Finally, you can estimate the total cost by breaking your project into small phases and estimate the work and material needed for those phases. Calculate the cost of work and material of the basement remodeling project phases than sum the costs up.</p>
<p>So these are the main basement remodeling cost estimation processes you can use.</p>
